{"tid":365891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眼鏡爛鬼左，後日就入camp，邊度配會快有得攞","createTime":"2017-08-19T15:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T16:31:29.000Z","uid":134497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81fd6071da640fec02811a09cccb416b1bb86fca","tid":365891,"uid":134497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"話說小弟整鬼爛左個眼鏡臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/230836_c277e96fba8319bb73964a6a4582e762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F230836_c277e96fba8319bb73964a6a4582e762.jpg&h=08a1f081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n副脈鏡而家鬆pel pel戴唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/230859_ff18a7a4f2208d345dc0c2e77063bd57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F230859_ff18a7a4f2208d345dc0c2e77063bd57.jpg&h=394e0485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想問有冇邊度可以淨配眼鏡臂，因為聽講啲眼鏡舖唔多肯做呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果冇，邊度有得配眼鏡係快有得攞，同埋啲款會唔會太舊<br />\n我後日就入camp好衰唔衰而家先黎爛眼鏡，有冇人好心解答下我，無限感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaa9881c5e2ad6d4d7e661bdd60ce1cf4aed148","tid":365891,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"入camp 叫組爸整咪得"},{"pid":"c2f57ef92b95d498de56f52707b374c20576c657","tid":365891,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"新輝有得即日拎<br />\n你打電話問下先<br />\n唔係間間分店可以即日攞<br />\n最快一個鐘內有得拎"},{"pid":"e07d99e8408df2318542e763d961dc061f648a18","tid":365891,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"帶c